      "Two attached dwellings sharing a common party wall",
      "3-4 bedroom configurations with flexible living spaces",
      "Private rear gardens for each dwelling",
      "Integrated car accommodation with garage or carport options",
      "Adaptable floor plans for slope conditions up to 1.35m",
      "Material palettes suited to diverse neighbourhood contexts"
    ],
    "ownershipTypes": ["torrens_title", "strata"],
